  28,12,"Na Y‚Äôadikan asi (Mose) kwan a Y‚Äôamma no annum (obiara nufu), enti (Mose nua baa no) kaa sŒµ: ‚ÄùMenkyerŒµ mo efie bi mufoÕª a wÕª‚ÄôbŒµtete no ama mo na wa‚ÄôhwŒµ no so yie?‚Äù"
